<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看着河面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不应该让师父他们上船的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我每次提醒他，他都不相信我。”悟净点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去看看那个男人把他们抓到哪里去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净跳进了河里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很快就到了一座洞府前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞府门上有个标志，写着“黑水河神府”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净用他的宝杖敲门。“开门！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门打开了，一个妖怪探出头来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想干什么？”妖怪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在找人。”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个和尚和一个长得像猪的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们被一个人抓走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们是被我抓走的。”妖怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你？”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”妖怪微笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要吃了唐僧好长生不老！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净用他的宝杖刺向妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪转了个身，用尾巴挡住了悟净的宝杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那尾巴的力气很大，差点儿把悟净打倒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪跳到了悟净身上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放开我！”悟净大叫。他推开了妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪又打了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净挥打着宝杖向水面游去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从水里跳了出来，落在悟空旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“下面有个妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净大口地喘着气说，“他很厉害。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空正要说话的时候，突然看见附近有人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那小船上的男人正向他们走来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134350</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抽出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么敢抓走我师父！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那人跪下，浑身发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不是我啊！”他大声说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是黑水河神，这是我的河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那妖怪变成了我的样子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空将金箍棒放回了耳朵里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我相信你。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161574</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道那妖怪是谁吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。”河神说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他看上去更害怕了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听说他的舅舅是龙王。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179626</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“那龙王是我的老朋友了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还有点儿怕我。我去和他谈谈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，悟空就出现在了龙宫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又见面了，悟空。”龙王笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“来我这里有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么让你的外甥占了黑水河？”悟空质问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙王的笑容不见了。“你在说什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的外甥占了黑水河。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空说，“现在他还要吃唐僧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，天啊。”龙王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道啊。我来处理。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和龙王飞到了黑水河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙王大叫：“外甥！出来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪从河里跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248848</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“舅舅！”他说，“您能来我太高兴了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是来玩儿的。”龙王大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是来带你回龙宫的。你会受到惩罚的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他低下了头，跟着龙王飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，河里水花四溅，河神出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧和八戒也出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，悟空。”河神说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不客气。”悟空说，“但是我们还是得过河。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那很简单。”河神说。他举起了手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>河水立即停止了流动，并形成了墙壁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空一行人从河床上走了过去，继续西行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>